      • put

        protected final void put(AbstractConfig.IKey key,
       Object value)
        puts a new config to the configuration map. If given value is default value of key then it will be removed. This is necessary to keep the ui code small and clean. Also the given value type will be asserted by AbstractConfig.IKey implementation.
        Parameters:
        key - mandatory parameter
        value - mandatory parameter
